<response><error><![CDATA[OK]]></error><limit>1</limit><offset>0</offset><number_of_page_results>1</number_of_page_results><number_of_total_results>1</number_of_total_results><status_code>1</status_code><results><abbreviation/><aliases/><api_detail_url><![CDATA[http://www.giantbomb.com/api/company/3010-1451/]]></api_detail_url><date_added>2008-04-01 01:39:32</date_added><date_founded/><date_last_updated>2012-01-19 07:36:17</date_last_updated><deck><![CDATA[Ikarion was a German developer and publisher active in the 1990s ]]></deck><description><![CDATA[<p>In 1993, the owner of <a data-ref-id="3010-3457" href="/kingsoft-gmbh/3010-3457/" slug="kingsoft-gmbh">Kingsoft</a> ( a German publisher and developer for budget games ), <a data-ref-id="3040-54115" href="/fritz-schafer/3040-54115/" slug="fritz-schafer">Fritz Schäfer</a>, decided to venture out and found a new major developer and publisher for Amiga and PC systems - Ikarion Software was born.</p><p>Their initial output of games consisted mainly of light-hearted business simulations (such as <a data-ref-id="3030-13949" href="/mad-news/3030-13949/" slug="mad-news">Mad News</a>, <a data-ref-id="3030-1515" href="/zeppelin-giants-of-the-sky/3030-1515/" slug="zeppelin-giants-of-the-sky">Zeppelin</a> or <a data-ref-id="3030-7768" href="/caribbean-disaster/3030-7768/" slug="caribbean-disaster">Caribbean disaster</a>). Later, they branched out and created puzzle games and fantasy-style wargames.</p><p>Schäfer eventually left the company and after changing hands a few times and failing to find further investments, the company finally shut down in 2011. However, one game had still been in development and after renaming the titles to '<a data-ref-id="3030-5153" href="/sacred/3030-5153/" slug="sacred">Sacred</a>' and finding a publisher in <a data-ref-id="3010-1239" href="/ascaron-entertainment-gmbh/3010-1239/" slug="ascaron-entertainment-gmbh">Ascaron</a>, they managed to save their reputation and release Sacred with great success.</p><p>The developers renamed to Studio 2 Software and have since released <a data-ref-id="3030-20901" href="/sacred-2-fallen-angel/3030-20901/" slug="sacred-2-fallen-angel">Sacred 2</a> and are working on a third instalment in the series.</p>]]></description><id>1451</id><image><icon_url><![CDATA[http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/square_avatar/0/3161/360536-ika.png]]></icon_url><medium_url><![CDATA[http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/scale_medium/0/3161/360536-ika.png]]></medium_url><screen_url><![CDATA[http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/screen_medium/0/3161/360536-ika.png]]></screen_url><small_url><![CDATA[http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/scale_small/0/3161/360536-ika.png]]></small_url><super_url><![CDATA[http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/scale_large/0/3161/360536-ika.png]]></super_url><thumb_url><![CDATA[http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/scale_avatar/0/3161/360536-ika.png]]></thumb_url><tiny_url><![CDATA[http://static.giantbomb.com/uploads/square_mini/0/3161/360536-ika.png]]></tiny_url></image><location_address/><location_city><![CDATA[Aachen]]></location_city><location_country><![CDATA[Germany]]></location_country><location_state/><name><![CDATA[Ikarion Software GmbH]]></name><phone><![CDATA[+49 241 47 01 50]]></phone><site_detail_url><![CDATA[http://www.giantbomb.com/ikarion-software-gmbh/3010-1451/]]></site_detail_url><website><![CDATA[http://www.ikarion.de/]]></website><developed_games><game><api_detail_url><![CDATA[http://www.giantbomb.com/api/game/3030-5805/]]></api_detail_url><id>5805</id><name><![CDATA[Demonworld]]></name><site_detail_url><![CDATA[http://www.giantbomb.com/demonworld/3030-5805/]]></site_detail_url></game><game><api_detail_url><![CDATA[http://www.giantbomb.com/api/game/3030-9723/]]></api_detail_url><id>9723</id><name><![CDATA[Demonworld: Dark Armies]]></name><site_detail_url><![CDATA[http://www.giantbomb.com/demonworld-dark-armies/3030-9723/]]></site_detail_url></game><game><api_detail_url><![CDATA[http://www.giantbomb.com/api